en:
But it matters not. I'll pry the serum
from your cold, dead hands if I must,
Velnorte.

My plays aren't popular enough
for us to afford anything extravagant,
but...

My back isn't the problem;
it's that big old empty space
between your ears!

Just thinking about it fills me with
a surge of emotion! It's too late;
I must express myself in song!

If you suddenly start wanting to repent
for all the evil things you've done,
it means you aren't gonna live long.

Well, I don't need him deciding things
for me. I'll choose my own dreams,
thank you.

Then maybe the rest of us oughta
try lending the Flamebringer a hand,
too.
